        <Summary>A free speech synthesizer</Summary>
        <Description>University of Edinburgh's  Festival Speech Synthesis Systems is a free software multi-lingual speech synthesis workbench that runs on multiple-platforms offering black box text to speech, as well as an open architecture for research in speech synthesis. It designed as a component of large speech technology systems.</Description>
